    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Trim the ends from the <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong>, then slice <strong>half </strong>finely</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining Brussels sprouts </strong>in<strong> </strong>half, lengthways</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
