            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and <strong>sliced garlic</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Meanwhile, combine the<strong> cider vinegar </strong>with<strong> </strong>2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
