      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and garlic has softened, add 2 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and give everything a good mix up until the flour has dissolved, then transfer to a plate and set aside for later</p><p>Reserve the pan</p>",
