      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced Brussels sprouts </strong>and <strong>halved Brussels sprouts </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften and char</p>",
