      "instruction": "<p>While the sprouts are cooking, add the <strong>linguine</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>linguine</strong> for 6-7 min (this will finish cooking in the sauce later!)</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>linguine</strong>,<strong> </strong>reserving 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[180ml]</span> <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Return the <strong>drained linguine</strong> to the pot and reboil half a kettle</p>",
